text: Jalali may refer to: ==People== * Jalali (surname) ==Places== * Jalali, Uttar Pradesh, a town and a nagar panchayat in Aligarh district in the state of Uttar Pradesh, India * Jalali, Uttarakhand, a small town situated in Almora district in the state of Uttarakhand, India * Jalali, Fars, a village in Fars Province, Iran * Jalali, Hormozgan, a village in Hormozgan Province, Iran * Jalali, Kerman, a village in Kerman Province, Iran * Jalali, alternate name of Bagh Jalal, a village in Kerman Province, Iran * Jalali, Razavi Khorasan, a village in Razavi Khorasan Province, Iran * Jalali, alternate name of Jalalieh, Razavi Khorasan, a village in Razavi Khorasan Province, Iran ==Other uses== * Jalali calendar, an Iranian calendar * Jalali (Kurdish tribe), a tribe of Eastern Turkey and Northwestern Iran
title: Jalali
